    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/1726ad40d36d2129a56ccc87f05d3a9c.webp?t=1746645456\" width=320 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An upcoming role-playing game centered around simulating the life of a bartender breathing life back into a run-down local city bar. Working night shifts, you will be tasked with pouring various cocktails for customers during fast-paced shifts, picked from a menu of your choosing. After each night, you will receive a payout depending on the quality of the drinks you poured. Using this money, you can customize the look and feel of the bar interior, your own apartment, as well as your player character. With thousands of player customization options and a branching narrative, you will be able to feel a sense of immersion as you maneuver your way through the story as it unfolds. Uncover the secrets of your manager, the shady landlord, as well as the mysterious &quot;last guy&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BE YOUR OWN BARTENDER</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/43d013050a64a1a01c72c6dbeb6b337f.poster.avif?t=1746645456\" width=560 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/43d013050a64a1a01c72c6dbeb6b337f.webm?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/43d013050a64a1a01c72c6dbeb6b337f.mp4?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>With thousands of possible character customization options, you can truly feel a part of the world you play in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR OWN BAR</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/86411c23fb79c5974a82da36f76ec5fc.poster.avif?t=1746645456\" width=482 height=482 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/86411c23fb79c5974a82da36f76ec5fc.webm?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/86411c23fb79c5974a82da36f76ec5fc.mp4?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate the walls, play your style of music, curate your own menu. The bar is never truly open until you feel right at home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BECOME YOUR OWN BOSS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/9a272e0c2e734463f5f127a689eda48a.poster.avif?t=1746645456\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/9a272e0c2e734463f5f127a689eda48a.webm?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/9a272e0c2e734463f5f127a689eda48a.mp4?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Make impactful narrative choices that decide the fate of the bar, its patrons, and your own story as it unfolds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BRING YOUR OWN BOOZE</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/6e1f8f7b094e9048a6ce94f744303287.poster.avif?t=1746645456\" width=392 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/6e1f8f7b094e9048a6ce94f744303287.webm?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/6e1f8f7b094e9048a6ce94f744303287.mp4?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase a high customer rating through an exciting physics-based gameplay system centered around fast-paced drink-making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLAST YOUR OWN BANGERS</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/c73de996da2ab2fd3d572265ec54ec98.poster.avif?t=1746645456\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/c73de996da2ab2fd3d572265ec54ec98.webm?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189710/extras/c73de996da2ab2fd3d572265ec54ec98.mp4?t=1746645456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>An extensive in-game music library containing songs from <i>Annie Jets</i>, <i>Chuuwee</i>, <i>The Have Nots</i>, <i>HEATSTROKE</i>, <i>Pleasure Nature</i>, <i>SEIZURE</i>, <i>Sylvan LaCue</i>, <i>Tired Mutt</i>, <i>Virginia Palms</i>, and <i>Xochitl</i>.</p>",
